show.title: Ek Din Ka CM
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/GqVRaQ
show.description:
When a fearless small-time YouTuber, known only as Common Man, exposes the Chief Minister’s right-hand goon in a viral sting, he ends up face-to-face with the state’s most powerful politician. In a heated live interview, the CM challenges him to prove he can do better — by becoming Chief Minister for one day.
What starts as a publicity stunt quickly turns into a gripping, high-stakes battle against corruption, red tape, and the very system he set out to question. From confronting shady contractors to exposing deadly negligence, Common Man’s single day in power forces him to choose between playing politics and saving lives — while the real CM, his cunning aides, and political enemies watch closely, waiting for him to fail.
